{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9ddc20622d","title":"无政府主义是对机会主义的惩罚","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d72c1727f5","index":0,"year":1967,"month":4,"day":null,"articleId":"9ddc20622d"}],"tags":[{"id":"1ae024ca96","name":"革命大联合","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1fd0be9388","type":"paragraph","text":"与X同志的一段对斋","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"9ddc20622d"},{"id":"fa4777a12e","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年四月）主席问：你们说是北京的大学大联合了，成立了红代会，很好呀！那三个司合部呢？","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"9ddc20622d"},{"id":"1ea11988d9","type":"paragraph","text":"答：没有了，都取消了。主席：啊，为什么要取消呀？我才不相信呢！已经取滑了","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"9ddc20622d"},{"id":"a780cefdd4","type":"paragraph","text":"（摘自周恩来同志1967年4月18日在广州群众组织座谈会的讲话）关于重管间题","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"9ddc20622d"},{"id":"7708889f19","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年四月）军管太少了。刘邓派工作组是压迫革命、反对群众，我们军管是支持革命的。","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"9ddc20622d"},{"id":"ed12ecb9ae","type":"paragraph","text":"（摘自谢富治副总理四月十八日讲话）关于革命派的大联合","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"9ddc20622d"},{"id":"22ba99724c","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年四月）","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"9ddc20622d"},{"id":"2e99f33789","type":"paragraph","text":"目前全国斗争形势很好，成绩很大，经验很多，全国都在前进中。革命派在优势情况下，可按系统、按部门、按单位实行大联合。但要注意保守派把造反派吃掉，不要用解散革命造反派的办法实行大联合。","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"9ddc20622d"},{"id":"1cb2898d8d","type":"paragraph","text":"接见富治同志时的款柔","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"9ddc20622d"},{"id":"5ee6e00099","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年四月十九日下午）我配贺你，祝贺这次大会的成功。请代向全北京市革命造反派祝贺。致敬电是全世界无产者联合超来的大宣言，就不要再搞宜言了。","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"9ddc20622d"},{"id":"60cf2506dc","type":"paragraph","text":"青年人要参加你们的工作，使前辈人不脱离群众，使青年人得到。青年人不能脱产，这样会造成脱离群众的，要牛官牛民。","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"9ddc20622d"},{"id":"379c4f05a5","type":"paragraph","text":"北京的形势还有反复，无政府主义就是机会主义的惩。要不怕犯错误，各种反动的观点和反动的群众组织是极少数的。就是反动组织也要做工作，但是还得斗争。","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"9ddc20622d"},{"id":"1a93c2e79e","type":"paragraph","text":"无政府主义是对机会主义的惩","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"9ddc20622d"},{"id":"740e0983d3","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年四月）","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"9ddc20622d"},{"id":"29b5e17f31","type":"paragraph","text":"过去的八条，现在的十条结合超来是对的。左派超来了，对立面也超来了，这也不要紧，有点反复有好处。无政府主义是对机会主义的惩留，要走向反面。","index":14,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"9ddc20622d"},{"id":"65fda272c5","type":"paragraph","text":"要把所有的联动放出来。·302。","index":15,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"9ddc20622d"}],"page":{"id":"2de52b1e1f","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"9ddc20622d","start":315,"end":315}}}},"__N_SSG":true}